{"tid":1624151,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發]為天琦刑期上訴眾籌！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-10-05T03:05:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T03:26:06.000Z","uid":68738,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"26220f9df3b2c5928dd79bf1d1fbc42b77a7f449","tid":1624151,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:05:12.000Z","msg":"【為天琦刑期上訴眾籌】<br />\n<br />\n各位愛護天琦的香港人：<br />\n<br />\n相信大家一直有關注天琦的消息，他的刑期上訴聆訊將於10月9日在高等法院審理。天琦的家人及好友慎重權衡後，決定聘請資深大律師代表天琦上訴。由於所費不菲，我們無奈之下發起眾籌，冀望聚沙成塔，目標金額為35萬，誠盼各位可與天琦同行。<br />\n<br />\n義工小組 敬上<br />\n<br />\n眾籌連結：<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/edwardleungappeal/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fedwardleungappeal%2F&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqoeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=98389900\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/edwardleungappeal/</a><br />\n眾籌目標：35萬港元（包括平台手續費6.9%，達標即止，為免加重大家的負擔，我們希望每人捐款不多於1000元）<br />\n<br />\n【Call for funding for Edward Leung's sentence appeal】<br />\n<br />\nDear fellow Hong Kongers,<br />\n<br />\nAs you all know, Edward&rsquo;s sentence appeal hearing will be held in the High Court on October 9. After much thought and consideration, we decided to hire a senior counsel to represent Edward in the appeal case. In order to cover the significant legal costs, we would like to raise HK$350,000 through crowdfunding. We sincerely hope that you could give Edward a hand and thank you in advance for your contribution.<br />\n<br />\nWith warmest regards,<br />\nEdward&rsquo;s Volunteer Team<br />\n<br />\nCrowdfunding link: <a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/edwardleungappeal/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fedwardleungappeal%2F&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqoeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=98389900\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/edwardleungappeal/</a><br />\nCrowdfunding target: HK$350,000 &ndash; including the platform handling fee of 6.9% and will end once the target is met. We advise that each person shall donate no more than HK$1,000.<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/71435848_752950941784411_2977189244172238848_n.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_oc=AQmuyS23Td9onaGuiplWauGB_hNrHHui_C4gYcILEuytEaMlkD0jmEx5W6K8DOwczT4&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=e94f7ff1085749596be1bf4920b502ee&amp;oe=5E290208\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F71435848_752950941784411_2977189244172238848_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26_nc_oc%3DAQmuyS23Td9onaGuiplWauGB_hNrHHui_C4gYcILEuytEaMlkD0jmEx5W6K8DOwczT4%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3De94f7ff1085749596be1bf4920b502ee%26oe%3D5E290208&h=95998cdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/leungtinkei/photos/a.172255923187252/752950935117745/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fleungtinkei%2Fphotos%2Fa.172255923187252%2F752950935117745%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqoeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=73e5c819\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/leungtinkei/photos/a.172255923187252/752950935117745/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"f2dbfef6489b11bdd60f78096cea485c11acef29","tid":1624151,"uid":263177,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:05:43.000Z","msg":"咪撚食人血啦"},{"pid":"a39b0106cf4a6e594a14622f03e84bdf4f7fd276","tid":1624151,"uid":68738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f2dbfef6489b11bdd60f78096cea485c11acef29","tid":1624151,"uid":263177,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:05:43.000Z","msg":"咪撚食人血啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:06:42.000Z","msg":"佢自己專頁po出黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc933d06d60c3e6cada352f04128c756d5672e8","tid":1624151,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:07:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/f